so alright, let’s practice! first, I’ll give a few sentences for you to translate

00:07:42.620 --> 00:07:42.620
into English.

00:07:43.620 --> 00:07:43.620
let’s start with a basic one. what does “olin li pona” mean?

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:48.160
[pause]

