did you say “sina olin”? if so, good job! if you said “*sina li olin”, remember,

00:08:36.569 --> 00:08:36.569
you don’t use li after mi or sina as subjects. as we saw in the last example, this doesn’t

00:08:40.789 --> 00:08:40.789
apply when they’re adjectives like in “moku mi,” since they aren’t the subjects themselves.

